  "detailed_description": "<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2707610/extras/0d40cff86e4cc0c5dda1ab18236dbf90.poster.avif?t=1709452355\" width=766 height=350 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2707610/extras/0d40cff86e4cc0c5dda1ab18236dbf90.webm?t=1709452355\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2707610/extras/0d40cff86e4cc0c5dda1ab18236dbf90.mp4?t=1709452355\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><strong>Desert Kingdoms</strong> is a simple medieval real-time strategy game in pixel art.<br><br>You will develop your villages, and conquer enemy kingdoms in procedurally generated skirmish maps.<br><br>Similar games to Desert Kingdoms: Eufloria and Mushroom Wars.<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Features:</h2>* Procedurally generated map which is different every time<br>* Different unit types with strengths and weaknesses<br>* Develop villages with different buildings<br>* Intense skirmishes<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2707610/extras/6817eeb30e46c69bd21cd38c62bcb5b7.poster.avif?t=1709452355\" width=600 height=438 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2707610/extras/6817eeb30e46c69bd21cd38c62bcb5b7.webm?t=1709452355\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2707610/extras/6817eeb30e46c69bd21cd38c62bcb5b7.mp4?t=1709452355\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2707610/extras/df7fd4433c2753a9234267b66ac69480.poster.avif?t=1709452355\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2707610/extras/df7fd4433c2753a9234267b66ac69480.webm?t=1709452355\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2707610/extras/df7fd4433c2753a9234267b66ac69480.mp4?t=1709452355\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span>",
  "about_the_game": "<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2707610/extras/0d40cff86e4cc0c5dda1ab18236dbf90.poster.avif?t=1709452355\" width=766 height=350 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2707610/extras/0d40cff86e4cc0c5dda1ab18236dbf90.webm?t=1709452355\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2707610/extras/0d40cff86e4cc0c5dda1ab18236dbf90.mp4?t=1709452355\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><strong>Desert Kingdoms</strong> is a simple medieval real-time strategy game in pixel art.<br><br>You will develop your villages, and conquer enemy kingdoms in procedurally generated skirmish maps.<br><br>Similar games to Desert Kingdoms: Eufloria and Mushroom Wars.<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Features:</h2>* Procedurally generated map which is different every time<br>* Different unit types with strengths and weaknesses<br>* Develop villages with different buildings<br>* Intense skirmishes<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2707610/extras/6817eeb30e46c69bd21cd38c62bcb5b7.poster.avif?t=1709452355\" width=600 height=438 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2707610/extras/6817eeb30e46c69bd21cd38c62bcb5b7.webm?t=1709452355\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2707610/extras/6817eeb30e46c69bd21cd38c62bcb5b7.mp4?t=1709452355\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2707610/extras/df7fd4433c2753a9234267b66ac69480.poster.avif?t=1709452355\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2707610/extras/df7fd4433c2753a9234267b66ac69480.webm?t=1709452355\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2707610/extras/df7fd4433c2753a9234267b66ac69480.mp4?t=1709452355\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span>",
